{"tid":1257442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 一人一post ] 626 朝早9點到夜晚9點！目標係G20 ! 一定要出！推","createTime":"2019-06-25T14:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T10:38:15.000Z","uid":94771,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5d685e935f50dff81b0b1ad0261dd9ac0b04eed3","tid":1257442,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"除左推人地626 既post, 大家可以<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">一人一post</span></span>推到<span style=\"color: orange;\">成頁都係626!</span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(懶既直接係最底copy再開！) </span></div><br />\n<br />\n我知出黎太密係唔好，係攰，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但626係一撚定要出！指向G20! </span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AtL9TTM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAtL9TTM.png&h=c54fd2cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[香港本地]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/26朝早9點</span></span>開始-野餐結束<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">日頭要多人，夜晚先會多人出！ </span></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8eWQDmp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8eWQDmp.png&h=c48e6ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MAW1K1U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMAW1K1U.png&h=5daa8179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/42qU417.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F42qU417.png&h=9c203f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmAU42L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmAU42L.png&h=9ef8f0f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[海外集氣 - 澳洲_墨爾本]<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/26晏晝5點</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/379KHQE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F379KHQE.png&h=704e7a08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">6/27朝早10點</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tu2HuuM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTu2HuuM.png&h=3d0a789c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">大家可以不同意，但記得不譴責！</div></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v91tp44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv91tp44.png&h=ff06b129&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">拒絕分化、槍口一致<br />\n對準殺人政權<br />\n不退不讓！</div></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190624/s00001/1561345247367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561345247367%2F&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDhZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=95f55516\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20190624%2Fs00001%2F1561345247367%2F&h=9752b627\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20190624/s00001/1561345247367/</a><br />\n【逃犯條例】外交部-中國不允許g20峰會討論香港<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">張軍強調，港府修訂《逃犯條例》</span>[size=2]<span style=\"color: teal;\">等一系列舉措，是維護社會公義，彌補法律制度缺陷，</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">是完全有必要的</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">，中央政府也會支持。</span></span>[/teal]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">張軍重申，香港是中國的特別行政區，</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港事務純屬中國內政，<span style=\"color: maroon;\">任何國家無權干預</span>。</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">口交部已經驚到出聲</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">各位香港人更加唔應該俾佢停<br />\n唔理用任何渠道都一定要draw多啲noise </div><br />\n令議會嘅事唔再局限喺立法會入面 而係連繫到香港街頭甚至海外<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">堅守底線，<br />\n因我們沒有退讓的理由。<br />\n<br />\n不撤不退！</div>"},{"pid":"0c24efe70c7710714de54a067be8740079d32e82","tid":1257442,"uid":111903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"8694e56eabc8c8a71178b0de928e853c40ebaa0c","tid":1257442,"uid":265066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86139604be77538ee6b1bf3cdc4217d647388e05","tid":1257442,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:52:25.000Z","msg":"推返626啲post上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日見"},{"pid":"bafbc7dc49214c2b2108dce044015e86f357fabe","tid":1257442,"uid":98926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"e2fd81d41792c91f25ecca05d72aa7add93dee87","tid":1257442,"uid":4619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T14:58:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719ae847c53993d703d20ac94be78a81a42a7da6","tid":1257442,"uid":190637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"大家明天見！"},{"pid":"7c60cc664c5d29c4408a15f9dd12440743511215","tid":1257442,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:10:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0900769f8ec52f6218a608c16a3dae418465abb3","tid":1257442,"uid":14305,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T15:24:07.000Z","msg":"希望唔好控時間 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早行完比大家休息下再晚9<